places.name: Pinel Island
places.perex: A tiny island with dreamy beaches, untouched nature and several nice beach restaurants. A great getaway.

places.name: Friar's Bay
places.perex: Small beach perfect for families with kids. The water is shallow and waves mild.

places.name: Marigot Market
places.perex: This local market is the most lively in the morning hours when the fishermen arrive with their share of fish and process them on the street.

places.name: Red Bay
places.name_suffix: Outermost regions of European Union, Fransa
places.perex: A beautiful beach with unusual, rather pinkish sand. A charming place just made for snorkelling and enjoying the sea.

places.name: The Butterfly Farm
places.name_suffix: Outermost regions of European Union, Fransa
places.perex: Visit to this garden is unexpectedly enjoyable - so many rare butterfly species can be seen flickering around!

places.name: Loterie Farm
places.perex: Unique natural reserve where you can experience extreme sports as well as the pristine nature.

places.name: Tintamarre Island
places.perex: A haven for avid snorkellers - the underwater life is so amazing. During the season, you can also spot turtles here!

places.name: Happy Bay Beach
places.name_suffix: Outermost regions of European Union, Fransa
places.perex: This beautiful white sand beach is surrounded by nature, shaded by trees. Perfect getaway for those who don't like busy spots.

places.name: Paradise Peak
places.perex: If you like hiking, you should not miss out the opportunity to climb the highest peak and overlook the whole island.

places.name: Orient Bay

places.name: Île Tintamarre
places.name_suffix: Outermost regions of European Union, Fransa
places.perex: Île Tintamarre is a small island with an area of approximately 0.8 square kilometres.

places.name: Hôtel Riu Palace
places.name_suffix: Outermost regions of European Union, Fransa

places.name: Anse Marcel
places.name_suffix: Outermost regions of European Union, Fransa

places.name: Club Orient Beach
places.perex: Clothing optional beach club with many facilities and things to do. Beautiful stretch of fine sand.

places.name: Grand Case Beach Club
places.name_suffix: Outermost regions of European Union, Fransa
places.perex: If you look for a special, luxurious beach experience, look no further. Lots of things to do, from water sports to shopping.

places.name: Le Ti Bouchon
places.name_suffix: Outermost regions of European Union, Fransa
places.perex: This restaurant boasts genuine French cuisine and pleasant, intimate atmosphere. Well worth trying.

places.name: Fort Saint Louis
places.perex: Climb the hill to overlook the city centre from an impressive ruins of colonial fortress. The largest historical remnant on the island.

places.name: Caribbean Paddling

places.name: Bell Point
places.name_suffix: Outermost regions of European Union, Fransa

places.name: Le Galion Beach
places.name_suffix: Outermost regions of European Union, Fransa
places.perex: The northern part of the beach has shallow water and is perfect for families. The other end is flocked by surfers.

places.name: Bistrot Caraibes
places.perex: May seem a bit on the expensive side - but the food they will serve you is totally worth it. French cuisine.

places.name: La Villa Restaurant
places.perex: This restaurant is perfect for special occasions. Mostly French cuisine is little spiced up by Caribbean approach.

places.name: American Tennis Academy
places.perex: This club has two lit tennis courses open to the visitors - come here if you are tired of the water sports!

places.name: Oyster Pond
places.perex: Picturesque marina lined with many interesting seafood restaurants. Come spend the evening here.
